Speaker 1: Hello?

Speaker 2: But the challenge I see is that Dr. Jommerbein has ordered the pharmacy to send you refills on a monthly basis.

Speaker 1: Do you want me to put a stop to that so you don't get them anymore?

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: Okay, one moment, sir.

Speaker 2: I'll take care of that.

Speaker 1: One moment, sir.

Speaker 2: Thank you.
